    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Peel and finely slice <strong>half </strong>your <strong>red onion[s]</strong>, chop your <strong>remaining red onion[s] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Add your <strong>sliced onion</strong> to a bowl and set aside for later</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based <strong>hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish </strong>over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
