    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crush your<strong> garlic</strong> open by squashing it with the side of a knife and remove the skin</p><p>Add your<strong> red wine vinegar</strong> to the bowl with the<strong> sliced red onion</strong> and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong></p>",
