        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> to the dish with your<strong> ras el hanout</strong> and <strong>harissa paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Add your<strong> beef stock mix </strong>with 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[400ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and bring to the boil over a high heat, then put the dish in the oven, uncovered, for 40 min or until the sauce has thickened and the lamb has cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>oven-baked spicy lamb stew</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
