      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> white long grain rice</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> with 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cover tightly with<strong> tin foil </strong>and put the dish on one side of a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 30 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>baked rice</strong></p>",
