    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the stew and rice are almost done, add your<strong> wholemeal pitta[s]</strong> to the other side of the tray and cook for a final 3-4 min or until warmed through</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? You may need 2 trays!</p>",
