    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, season the <strong>oven-baked spicy lamb stew</strong> with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and drizzle over your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> quick-pickled red onion</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>warmed pitta </strong>and <strong>baked rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
